你可以看到。

11
00:00:32,119 --> 00:00:33,720
And the gap has a name.
这个差距有个名字。

12
00:00:33,720 --> 00:00:36,599
Today, we are going to close the gap.
今天，我们要缩小这个差距。

13
00:00:36,599 --> 00:00:40,000
The 47% isn't a failure of the technology,
47%并不是技术的失败，

14
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,639
is the absence of framework.
而是缺乏框架。

15
00:00:42,639 --> 00:00:46,599
92% of students now use the AI regularly.
现在92%的学生定期使用AI。

16
00:00:46,599 --> 00:00:49,060
Adoption isn't a question anymore,
采用不再是一个问题，

17
00:00:49,060 --> 00:00:51,400
but adoption is not fluency.
但采用并不等于流利。

18
00:00:51,400 --> 00:00:54,720
And the most people have never been clearly shown
而大多数人从未清楚地看到

19
00:00:54,720 --> 00:00:57,919
what the difference between them actually looks like.
它们之间的区别是什么样的。

20
00:00:57,919 --> 00:01:01,279
The question is no longer why the people are using AI.
问题不再是人们为什么使用AI。

21
00:01:01,279 --> 00:01:04,120
The question is, are they using it well?
问题是，他们是否使用得当？

22
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:09,540
Right now, most people fall into one of two patterns.
现在，大多数人落入两种模式之一。

23
00:01:09,540 --> 00:01:11,239
They're either overwhelmed,
他们要么感到不知所措，

24
00:01:11,239 --> 00:01:14,800
